pffft
Class OldClient

java.lang.Object
  pffft.OldClient

public class OldClient
extends Object

A direct peer-to-peer text/audio/video program.

This is the latest stable release that is mostly in one class. As of version 1.6, the program was split up into several smaller ones for the sake of easier programming. It remains here for the sake of testing and backwards compatibility.

Version:
beta 1.5b7a
Author:
George Aleksandrovich
